{"type": "article", "id": 16047, "title": "空气净化器", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-14T07:08:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115212mfhVLlo6IcHgJdMG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是两套空气净化器，来自荷兰设计师 Fabian Zeijler 。“momentum” 由浅蓝色的水滴、白色的半球体和黑色的碟状物组成，分别测量湿度、通风与颗粒物，当“momentum”感应到不良空气时，就启动旋转运动模式，开启室内门窗，蒸发水分以过滤室内空气。“pūrificātum”是内含照明的净化器，有立式和台式两种和暖白和冷白两种灯光，能直接用做照明灯，它的特殊功能在调整净化器的角度以改变室内气流方向。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143438NEMseZHhdXAYcGP8.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"689\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.84229829\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143438qvCToKmkrlLQ62xW.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"690\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143439U4hxn1ejtTNJZuzA.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"955\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.16748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143439irG2KsoP45m0pTAI.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"690\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143440eqtn4z5oDUIiNZsd.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"544\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}